\/\/speed 1<b>, <b>without measuring cup<b>."},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Add all remaining jam ingredients, except bourbon, and cook <b>40 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>, <b>without measuring cup<b>."},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Add bourbon and cook for a further <b>80 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>, <b>without measuring cup<b>. Transfer into a sealable container and allow to cool before placing into refrigerator until ready to use (jam will thicken as it cools)."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Eggs"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Grease 4 egg rings with oil and set aside. Line Varoma tray with a piece of wet and well-wrung baking paper, ensuring paper goes all the way to the edges. Place water into mixing bowl, then place Varoma into position and insert Varoma tray."},{"isHeader":false,"content":"Place egg rings onto baking paper and crack 1 egg into each ring. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>8-10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b> or until eggs are cooked to your liking."},{"isHeader":false,"content":"To serve, slice bagels in half horizontally, spread with bacon jam and top with an egg."}],"usefulItems":"ceramic or glass bowl, baking paper, baking tray (30 x 40 cm), kitchen towel, silicone bread mat, pastry brush, sealable container, 4 egg rings, oven, refrigerator","id":"r82175","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-ahace-ffDk8\/XZaf6GwIMEI\/AAAAAAAAgzU\/vtxJuSTkpjAnOQw64loQV2mTTyW6ecFwACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_yNi6tOsHaM3YeeV7.png","title":"Bagels with bacon jam and egg","ingredients":[{"isHeader":true,"content":"Ingredients"},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Bagels"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"olive oil, for greasing"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"920 g water, plus 1 tbsp extra for egg wash"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"250 g full cream milk"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"1 tbsp raw sugar"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"3 tsp dried instant yeast"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"520 g baker's flour, plus extra for dusting"},{"isHeader":false,"content":"3 tsp sea salt"},{"isHeader":fa